  "_comment": "Per-stage beatmap data. beats_per_bar defines the timing grid AttackFrames reads via RhythmTrack. accent_beats mark the downbeats that trigger the on_beat_damage_multiplier window. The window itself is config.match_rules.on_beat_window_beats wide (default 0.125 = 1/8 beat either side of accent).",
